OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy start, with
OL,6,Fblustery showers, although some
OL,7,Fbrighter spells mainly in the east.
OL,8,FSunny spells developing more widely in
OL,9,Fthe afternoon, with showers gradually
OL,10,Fdying out. Feeling warm in the
OL,11,Fafternoon sunshine, but this tempered
OL,12,Fby strong winds.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FMostly dry this evening with
OL,15,Fsunny spells and wind easing. Cloud
OL,16,Fthickening overnight, with rain
OL,17,Farriving before dawn. Wind
OL,18,Fstrengthening a little again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
