OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FCloudy, damp and breezy but
OL,6,Fwarm. Rain will be persistent,
OL,7,Fpossibly heavy in the morning,
OL,8,Fbecoming more confined to western
OL,9,Fparts in the afternoon. Some
OL,10,Fbrightness possible in the east.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMuch
OL,13,Fwarmer during this period. Friday,
OL,14,Fwarm or very warm with hazy sunshine.
OL,15,FSaturday remaining warm with sunny
OL,16,Fspells. Perhaps more cloudy with rain
OL,17,Flater Sunday, but still warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
